<BaseLayout
  title="Contact | BeaconGuard Assurance"
  description="Request a controlled architecture evaluation for regulated workflows that need policy enforcement, approved-pathway checks, needs-review routing, or audit-ready evidence before model execution."
>
  <section class="stack-section">
    <h1>Request a Controlled Architecture Evaluation</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Use this contact route to discuss a regulated workflow where AI or automation needs deterministic policy enforcement, approved-pathway checks, needs-review routing, or audit-ready evidence before model execution. BeaconGuard deploys alongside existing applications and does not require replacing the systems that already own workflow logic or records.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="stack-section">
    <h2>Inquiry Type</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Healthcare Architecture / Privacy Review</li>
      <li>Financial / AML Platform Review</li>
      <li>Regulated Internal Automation Review</li>
      <li>Security Architecture Review</li>
      <li>General Partnership Inquiry</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="stack-section">
    <h2>Who should contact BeaconGuard</h2>
    <div class="section-grid">
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>Healthcare</h3>
